OL,3,C'People assume I'm on drugs' - man
OL,4,Cwith cerebral palsy on discrimination
OL,6,FA Somerset man has spoken out about
OL,7,Fwhat he says is regular discrimination
OL,8,Fhe faces because he has cerebral palsy.
OL,10,FNik Royale, who lives near Shepton
OL,11,FMallet, says he is often accused of
OL,12,Fbeing drug or on drugs and it can lead
OL,13,Fto him being denied entry into venues
OL,14,Fand events.
OL,16,FThe 51-year-old lives independently
OL,17,Fand is a qualified climbing instructor.
