OL,3,C'People assume I'm on drugs' - man
OL,4,Cwith cerebral palsy on discrimination
OL,6,FNik wants to see better access for
OL,7,Fdisabled people across the country and
OL,8,Fbetter education so that young people
OL,9,Fwith the condition.
OL,11,FHe said: "With cerebral palsy, it
OL,12,Fdoesn't mean we can't do anything it
OL,13,Fjust means we have to go about it a
OL,14,Fdifferent way and nine times out of 10
OL,15,Fwe overcome it.
OL,17,F"We have people in Emmerdale now,
OL,18,FCoronation Street that have cerebral
OL,19,Fpalsy. For me to see them - when I was
OL,20,Fthere age none of that was possible.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
